<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0736a20shiFaShen"><lb
ed="T" n="0736a20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0736a20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011644"><placeName>錢塘</placeName><placeName>天竺寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A004183">法詵</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0736a21"/><persName key="A004183">釋法詵</persName>，姓<name>孫</name>氏<ptr target="#n305"/>。母初夢吞明珠，遂黜魚惡<lb
ed="T" n="0736a22"/>葷。誕彌厥月<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g481"/>，生有異表。<date key="j19884171988782" from-iso="+0732-01-01" to-iso="+0732-12-31">十五</date>辭親從師，依<lb
ed="T" n="0736a23"/>年受具。行學一集，蔚為教宗，卷<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g783"/><persName key="A012898">伊</persName>、<persName key="A003202">呂</persName>立功<lb
ed="T" n="0736a24"/>之致，陋<persName key="A012741">黃</persName>、<persName key="A012739">綺</persName>肆志<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g782"/>之適。遺形理性<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g784"/>，與山木<lb
ed="T" n="0736a25"/>為群。故地<persName key="A009437">恩貞<roleName>大師</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n306"/>囑之以《華嚴經》、《菩薩戒》、<lb
ed="T" n="0736a26"/>《起信論》<ptr target="#n3277"/>，心以靜<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>銑</sic><corr>銳</corr></choice><ptr target="#n786"/>，智與經冥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g787"/>。一夕夢乘大<lb
ed="T" n="0736a27"/>艑<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g788"/>，直截滄溟，橫山當前，峻與天極。不覺孤<lb
ed="T" n="0736a28"/>帆鳶戾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g789"/>，懷襄上濟<ptr type="glossary" target="#g790"/><ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n791"/>，峯竦竦而忽<anchor xml:id="beg0736002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>高</sic><corr>焉</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0736002"/>，雲溶溶而<lb
ed="T" n="0736a29"/>在下。既寤，形若委衣<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g792"/>，流汗輕醒。自此，句義<pb ed="T" n="0736b" xml:id="T50.2061.0736b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0736b01"/>不思而得，一部全文常現心境，「事事無礙」之<lb
ed="T" n="0736b02"/>旨，如貫<anchor xml:id="beg0736sgsz2"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0736sgsz2"/><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g793"/>焉。<date from-iso="+0747-02-18" key="j19939441994298" to-iso="+0748-02-07"><name>天寶</name>六年</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000009888"><placeName>蘇州</placeName><placeName>常樂寺</placeName></placeName>繢<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g794"/><lb
ed="T" n="0736b03"/><persName key="A004206">盧舍那</persName>像，化示群品。<date from-iso="+0767-02-08" key="j20012392001592" to-iso="+0768-01-27"><name>大曆</name>二年</date><ptr target="#n795"/>，於<placeName key="PL000000009711"><placeName>常州</placeName><placeName>龍興<lb
ed="T" n="0736b04"/>寺</placeName></placeName>講，纔登法座，忽有異光如曳紅縷，漸<lb
ed="T" n="0736b05"/>明漸大，縈旋杳空。久修行者會中先覩。前<lb
ed="T" n="0736b06"/>後講大經十遍，撰《<anchor xml:id="beg0736003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>儀</sic><corr>義</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0736003"/>記》十二卷。<date key="j20055562005556" when-iso="+0778-12-04"><name>大曆</name>十三<lb
ed="T" n="0736b07"/>年十一月七日</date>，沙門<persName key="A021878">慧覺</persName>夢巨塔陷地二級。<lb
ed="T" n="0736b08"/>無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，<persName key="A004183">詵</persName>示疾而終，春秋六十一，慧命四十<lb
ed="T" n="0736b09"/>二<ptr target="#n307"/>。受法弟子<persName key="A009464">太初</persName>，付以香<anchor xml:id="beg0736sgsz3"/>罏<anchor xml:id="end0736sgsz3"/>、談柄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g796"/>，<placeName key="PL000000018846"><anchor xml:id="beg0736sgsz4"/>潯<anchor xml:id="end0736sgsz4"/>陽</placeName><persName key="A009465">正覺</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0736b10"/><placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName><persName key="A009457">神秀</persName>，亦猶<name>儒</name>氏之有<persName key="A021880">游</persName>、<persName key="A010088">夏</persName>焉。<persName key="A004183">詵</persName>初講<lb
ed="T" n="0736b11"/><placeName key="PL000000011644">天竺寺</placeName>，盛闡《華嚴》。時<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>僧<persName key="A001755">澄觀</persName>就席決疑，<lb
ed="T" n="0736b12"/>深得幽趣<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g428"/>。及終，<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName><persName key="A008833">皎然</persName>為碑，<placeName key="PL000000010783">䢴城</placeName><persName key="A001081">肅<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n158"/><lb
ed="T" n="0736b13"/>為頌，合揚其美哉。</p>
